    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>When you say you increased <code>MAVEN_OPTS</code>, what values did you increase? Did you increase the <code>MaxPermSize</code>, as in example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>export MAVEN_OPTS=\"-Xmx512m -XX:MaxPermSize=128m\"\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>(or on Windows:)</p>\n\n<pre><code>set MAVEN_OPTS=-Xmx512m -XX:MaxPermSize=128m\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can also specify these JVM options <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/35998748/32453\">in each maven project separately</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
